    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a thrilling adventure through a mesmerizing and ever-changing folding city. Your mission? Navigate the labyrinthine streets and overcome obstacles to uncover the city's secrets and find a way to escape before everything collapses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303140/extras/093893e21162ad586b1157d2a965908c.avif?t=1770260298\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303140/extras_big/093893e21162ad586b1157d2a965908c.avif?t=1770260298 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Explore and Collect:</strong> </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather essential items and pieces of information that will aid your journey.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Dynamic Environment:</strong> </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a city that folds and shifts around you, keeping you on your toes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>High-Stakes Adventure:</strong> </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every moment counts as you race against time to avoid being caught in the city's final collapse.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you make it out before the city crushes everything in its path? Find out in this captivating and intense short adventure game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303140/extras/b8b64db4098bf393470b843987498b8d.avif?t=1770260298\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303140/extras_big/b8b64db4098bf393470b843987498b8d.avif?t=1770260298 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This game is created by <strong>@LittleMaru</strong> with YAHAHA Horror Game Kit and YAHAHA assists the creator with packaging and publishing the game based on their request. Yahaha Horror Gamekit is tailored for imaginative creators and players who adore horror games, all without the need for any programming expertise.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303140/extras/3a8a0be266c6899aef1750ef08bd9bbb.avif?t=1770260298\" width=720 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
